A little help please I removed old gmapprom.img renamed gmapsupp,img to gmapprom.img and copied into Garmin dir on SD it was to big to put in original device dir. no worky

On the SD use the gmapsupp.img filename.
Be sure the file has not double extension (gmapsupp.img.img), check the file proprierties.
Got it to work by renaming mexico file gmapprom.img and put it in Garmin dir internal.Then copied USA file into SD Garmin dir as gmapsupp.img THANKS.. Now have Mexico and USA maps both working !!
